parameters: \SE[14] Huh, what was that just now...?

\SE[3]What was that... It was a stepping stone. \!\SE[1]Was
it your first time, Vita?
\SE[8]Huh... No, not that... \SE[44]Can I say this...?

\SE[68]Something... Laura's jumping sound... Isn't it too
unique...?

\SE[109]Huh... Huh...? \SE[93]Is it really that strange...?
\SE[95]What does Lunaroa think about my jumping sound...?

\SE[102]Ah...! It's a treasure chest!! Hurry, we need to
open it...!!

\SE[40]Oh, it's heavy...!? \SE[92]Is this... a flail?
\SE[51]There's no way I can wield something like this...

\SE[4]I might be able to use it. \!\SE[3]...Um, can I borrow
it for a moment?

\SE[5]Sure, but... be careful, okay? \SE[3]It's really
heavy, you know?

Vita is able to wield heavy weapons because she has strong
power.

The normal attack changes depending on the weapon. With the
giant sword, it allows for follow-up attacks from allies.
With the iron ball, it performs three random attacks. With
the bow, it enables high-speed area attacks.

Since it can be used with 'No Cost', let's use it according
to the situation and switch it up!
\SE[2]Like this. Got it? \SE[1]See, I'm useful, right?
\SE[102]Oh, you're quite something for being so young...
